Source code : https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/

Firefox is a popular web browser, built with Gecko
It was quite popular before the release of Google Chrome

Pros[+]:
-Not another Chromium based browser
-Open source
-Good extension support, unlike Google Chrome's Manifest v3 engine
-Actually good UI and customization options, especially with userChrome.css for experienced users
-Built in tree tabs


Cons[-]:
-Sometimes it has memory leaks
-Because all web is designed for Chrome, sometimes it has webpage rendering issues, but its really rare in 2024

